It underlines the importance of checking the presence of bats before proceeding with the maintenance of the properties, because by destroying it unwittingly a single maternity nest, it can cause the death of 400 females and young, or even the disappearance of an entire local population.
Fleas are protected and it is illegal to kill them, disturb them, or destroy their umbrellas.
